EigenLayer unveils a partnership with UMA and Polymarket

EigenLayer joined forces with UMA $UMA and Polymarket to develop a next-generation oracle system, improving the reliability and functionality of prediction market oracles. EigenLayer will leverage its restaking mechanism and $EIGEN token to support the new oracle system, while UMA contribute decentralized financial contracts and Polymarket will provide its expertise.

The new oracle system will operate on ‚Äúintersubjective truth,‚Äù using community consensus instead of objective data. This makes it especially suitable for prediction markets where the resolution of bets depends on widely accepted interpretations of events.

Top 5 Overbought + Oversold Tokens ‚Äî 1st October 2024

Today, I analyzed the Relative Strength Index (RSI) of more than 500 tokens.

The RSI is a momentum indicator that measures the speed and change of price movements. It is calculated as a value between 1 and 100, helping traders identify overbought or oversold conditions.

A high RSI (>70) suggests the asset may be overbought and due for a pullback, while a low RSI (<30) indicates it could be oversold and ready for a potential bounce.
